                 "whatCopy":  "Proof of Contribution Г© um painel open-source que rastreia pull requests mescladas em ecossistemas cripto. Ele transforma dados pГєblicos do GitHub em um mapa de contribuiГ§Гµes pesquisГЎvel e filtrГЎvel, mostrando quem constrГіi, onde contribui e quais projetos concentram atividade open-source.",
                 "faqMergedAnswer":  "Merged PRs represent accepted contributions вЂ” work that was reviewed and integrated. This provides a clearer signal of meaningful contribution than raw activity metrics such as issues or comments.",
